# Implementation Plan - FAQ Generator MicroSaaS

## Goal Description
Develop a MicroSaaS web application that accepts a URL, scrapes its content, and uses AI to intelligently generate relevant FAQ questions and answers.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **AI Provider**: I plan to use **OpenAI (GPT-4o)** for the intelligence layer. You will need to provide an `OPENAI_API_KEY`. Is this acceptable?
>
> **Tech Stack Confirmation**:
> - **Framework**: Next.js (React) for a robust full-stack app.
> - **Styling**: Vanilla CSS (Custom, Premium Design).
> - **Scraping**: `cheerio` (lightweight) or `puppeteer` (if JS rendering needed). Starting with `cheerio`.

## Proposed Changes
### Phase 1: Foundation
- [ ] Initialize Next.js project in `~/Documents/FAQ_Generator`.
- [ ] Set up premium design system (CSS variables, typography, dark mode).

### Phase 2: Core Logic (API)
- [ ] Create API route `/api/generate`.
- [ ] Implement URL fetching and text extraction.
- [ ] Integrate OpenAI API to generate FAQs from text.

### Phase 3: User Interface
- [ ] Build a high-converting Landing/Input page.
- [ ] Create a "Results" view to display generated FAQs.
- [ ] Add "Copy to Clipboard" and "Export" features.

## Verification Plan
- **Manual**: Test with various URLs (blogs, landing pages, documentation).
- **Quality**: Verify FAQs are relevant and accurate to the source text.
